  "description": "<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">Application:</span></strong><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">Universal Titanium Header Exhaust Heat Wrap, fit for most Go Kart, Dirt Bike, Cars, Trucks, Motorcycle.</span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">Features:</span></strong><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Comes one roll of 50ft long header exhaust heat wrap with 10 pieces stainless steel zip ties</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Made of high quality Lava Rock Fiberglass</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Wrap dimension: 50 ft (length) x 2\" (width) x 1/12\" (thickness)</span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Zip Ties dimension: 300 mm (length) x 5 mm (width)</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-To withstand continuous high temperature up to 2000¡ãF</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Can reduce under-hood temperature about 50%-70%, prevent from burns</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Cooler air in the engine bay and increased flow provides better performance</span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-High resistance to abrasions, oil spills, temperatures and vibration breakdown</span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Extremely pliable for a tight and secure wrap</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-Installation instruction does not included</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-100% Brand New Items, Never Used Or Installed</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">-1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">Package Included:</span></strong> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">1 ROLL x 2 in*50 ft Titanium Header Exhaust Heat Wrap</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">10 x Stainless Steel Zip Ties</span> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">Why we need Heat Wrap:</span></strong> \n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:΢ÈíÑźÚ;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;\">\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">Heat Wrap for exhaust or headers is important for controlling temperatures and reducing the radiant heat under your hood. It can be also used for the exhaust to keeping the gasses hotter within the exhaust system. It will also help in decreasing density and increase the flow of exhaust gases. This will lead to a reduction intake temperatures. </span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt;\">By using Heat Wrap will be able to have in increase in horsepower based on the application. Our wraps are made of high quality Lava Rock Fiberglass to improve heat retention and withstand heat up to 2000¡ãF.</span> \n\t</p>\n</div>",
